name: AntEater (itch) (lazydevtom)
description:
Controls;

WASD to move

Left Click to eat ant and punch trees

Gameplay:

Your health will down every second if you don't eat anything or get stronger

Eating ants and punching trees will heal you

Powerups:

Increase your speed
Heals you
Makes your stronger

This my first game I made for a jam so have fun :D
